<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>电商 on 大大的小蜗牛</title><link>https://www.eallion.com/tags/%E7%94%B5%E5%95%86/</link><description>Recent content in 电商 on 大大的小蜗牛</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-cn</language><copyright>© 2006 - 2024 &lt;span class='inline-block'>&lt;a href='https://www.eallion.com/copyright/' target='_blank'>eallion.com&lt;/a> All Rights Reserved&lt;/span>. &lt;span class='inline-block'>&lt;a href='https://beian.miit.gov.cn/' target='_blank'>浙ICP备16031768号-2&lt;/a>&lt;/span></copyright><lastBuildDate>Mon, 19 Jan 2015 10:37:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://www.eallion.com/tags/%E7%94%B5%E5%95%86/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>运营小记 - 电商的本质 - 20150119</title><link>https://www.eallion.com/20150119/</link><pubDate>Mon, 19 Jan 2015 10:37:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.eallion.com/20150119/</guid><description>文章讨论了电商的本质，指出电商实际上就是做买卖，没有太多技巧可言。工具只能提高效率，但不能取代人的智慧。作者呼吁回归本源，不要追求投机取巧。</description><media:content xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://www.eallion.com/20150119/featured.png"/></item><item><title>运营小记 - 关联销售一例</title><link>https://www.eallion.com/guan-lian-xiao-shou/</link><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2013 11:12:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.eallion.com/guan-lian-xiao-shou/</guid><description>文章讲述了一个关于关联销售的实例。一所学校给孩子们发放免费游泳票，但家长必须购买门票才能陪同孩子进入游泳馆。这个例子说明了免费发放的儿童票只是为了吸引家长成为真正的客户，从而实现关联销售。</description><media:content xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://www.eallion.com/guan-lian-xiao-shou/featured.png"/></item><item><title>运营小记 20130506</title><link>https://www.eallion.com/20130506/</link><pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2013 21:55:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.eallion.com/20130506/</guid><description>文章内容是关于运营和推广的小记，提到了阿里巴巴入股新浪微博、电商 2.0 时代来临等话题。</description><media:content xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://www.eallion.com/20130506/featured.png"/></item><item><title>评估报告：机会只有 50%</title><link>https://www.eallion.com/pgbg/</link><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2013 19:41:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.eallion.com/pgbg/</guid><description>文章内容是关于一个评估报告，指出成功的机会只有 50%。文章提到了电商行业的一些问题，如缺乏 ERP 系统、分销渠道减少、团购成本高等。作者还强调决策权和执行力之间的矛盾，并表示时间成本是他面临的主要风险。最后，作者认为成功与否取决于关系磨合，不能轻率地做出决定。</description><media:content xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://www.eallion.com/pgbg/featured.png"/></item></channel></rss>